<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>E-portfolio Evan Chavot B2</title>

    <style>
        /* ---------------------------------------------------
           PATTERN AURORA
        --------------------------------------------------- */
        .container {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: radial-gradient(
                    ellipse at 20% 30%,
                    rgba(138, 43, 226, 0.8) 0%,
                    rgba(138, 43, 226, 0) 60%
                ),
                radial-gradient(
                    ellipse at 80% 50%,
                    rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.7) 0%,
                    rgba(0, 191, 255, 0) 70%
                ),
                radial-gradient(
                    ellipse at 50% 80%,
                    rgba(50, 205, 50, 0.6) 0%,
                    rgba(50, 205, 50, 0) 65%
                ),
                linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #0a0520 100%);
            background-blend-mode: overlay, screen, hard-light;
            z-index: -10;
            animation: aurora-drift 25s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
        }

        .container::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(
                    45deg,
                    rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02) 0px,
                    rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02) 1px,
                    transparent 1px,
                    transparent 40px
                ),
                repeating-linear-gradient(
                    -45deg,
                    rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 0px,
                    rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 1px,
                    transparent 1px,
                    transparent 60px
                );
            animation: grid-shift 20s linear infinite;
        }

        .container::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: radial-gradient(
                circle at center,
                transparent 70%,
                rgba(10, 5, 32, 0.8) 100%
            );
            animation: aurora-pulse 8s infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes aurora-drift {
            0% { background-position: 0% 0%; filter: hue-rotate(0deg); }
            50% { background-position: -10% -5%; filter: hue-rotate(30deg) brightness(1.2); }
            100% { background-position: 5% 10%; filter: hue-rotate(60deg); }
        }

        @keyframes grid-shift {
            0% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
            100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }
        }

        @keyframes aurora-pulse {
            0% { opacity: 0.8; transform: scale(1); }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1.05); }
            100% { opacity: 0.8; transform: scale(1); }
        }

        /* ---------------------------------------------------
           TYPO & GLOBAL
        --------------------------------------------------- */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #eee;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* ---------------------------------------------------
           TITRES
        --------------------------------------------------- */
        h1 {
            font-size: 3.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: #cfcfcf;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            max-width: 650px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* ---------------------------------------------------
           BOUTONS
        --------------------------------------------------- */
        .button-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .fancy-btn {
            width: 185px;
            height: 65px;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            border: none;
            position: relative;
            background: #100720;
            transition: 0.15s;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .fancy-btn::after {
            content: '';
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: radial-gradient(
                circle farthest-corner at 10% 20%,
                rgba(255,94,247,1) 17.8%,
                rgba(2,245,255,1) 100.2%
            );
            filter: blur(18px);
            z-index: -1;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
        }

        .fancy-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
        }

        .fancy-btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.92) rotate(2deg);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container"></div>

<div class="content">

    <h1>E-portfolio Evan Chavot B2</h1>
    <h2>Bienvenue sur mon espace professionnel</h2>

    <p>Vous trouverez ici toutes les informations essentielles me concernant : mon parcours, mes compétences et mes motivations. Cet e-portfolio a pour objectif de vous présenter mon profil de manière claire et organisée.</p>

    <p>Choisissez une des sections ci-dessous pour commencer :</p>

   <div class="button-container">
    <button class="fancy-btn">CV</button>
    <button class="fancy-btn">En savoir plus</button>
    <button class="fancy-btn">Pourquoi un BUT RT ?</button>
    <button class="fancy-btn">Portfolio</button>
</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>